WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:21.259
Hey, good morning family. I have another video for you. There is going to be a celebrity that's very influential and popular. I saw a plot, and this is heavy again with the demonic.

00:00:21.260 --> 00:00:37.229
They will pretend to be born again, and they will start preaching the gospel, saying that Jesus Christ is Lord and he died for you.

00:00:37.230 --> 00:00:55.916
They're going to come out real strong with that. Then I saw months go by, and they start preaching a universal gospel—that whatever you believe in is okay.

00:00:55.917 --> 00:01:07.572
Because they preached this gospel first about Jesus being the only way to get to heaven, everybody believes it. Christians were naive, like they always are.

00:01:07.573 --> 00:01:16.884
I hate to say this, but a lot of times they just accept everybody really quick and are naive about not discerning and seeing things in the spirit realm.

00:01:16.885 --> 00:01:25.510
They are always real quick to follow the leader. We've got to be discerning; we have to be wise as serpents.

00:01:25.511 --> 00:01:41.688
You need to be very discerning in these last days because the enemy is going to send people to try to corrupt and trick people into following a false gospel.

00:01:41.689 --> 00:01:56.530
Celebrity deception. I saw this celebrity—I won't name the person because it's not wisdom—come on the scene.

00:01:56.531 --> 00:02:06.735
I know exactly who it is, and it's somebody big in the pop world. Teenagers are going to fall for this big time.

00:02:06.736 --> 00:02:23.415
As parents, you need to be very watchful of music and the things that are happening because they're going to come on the scene, and because they're already huge in the pop world, this is going to sway a lot of people.

00:02:23.416 --> 00:02:31.499
Like I said, they come on and everything seems to be good. People say we can't judge them, it's under grace, let them have their time.

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:45.958
Everybody is trying to just accept them and love them, but then they start preaching that Buddha is the way to heaven, all these other religions, and that everything's okay—that we're all linked to one and serving one God.

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:50.138
All this other trash they're going to start spewing out of their mouth.

00:02:50.139 --> 00:02:56.724
I saw this coming; this was a prophetic warning that this person is coming.

00:02:56.725 --> 00:03:14.322
Don't be deceived just because they're a celebrity and they say they have Jesus. Use wisdom and discernment, and let Jesus be your guide.

00:03:14.323 --> 00:03:27.984
Just because they're popular and cool, don't let that be an influence on your life. Follow the voice of the Lord in these last days.

00:03:27.985 --> 00:03:36.899
The Lord warned me also, saying, 'Brandon, there's going to be false prophets.'He said he told us there would be many false prophets coming.

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:56.139
If you look at what's going on on YouTube right now—and I honestly don't watch a lot of other people on YouTube—there is a prophetic brother on every single channel.

00:03:56.140 --> 00:04:00.372
I didn't realize what was going on over here; this is absolutely insane.

00:04:00.373 --> 00:04:09.598
I'm not saying all these people aren't hearing God—maybe some of them are—but I'm just saying there are a lot of voices saying all kinds of different stuff.

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:20.205
It's very alarming to me. The Lord told me, 'Do you not see the scriptures being fulfilled right in front of your face, son?

00:04:20.206 --> 00:04:30.343
There are many false prophets.'What's amazing is a lot of them are charismatic.

00:04:30.344 --> 00:04:37.517
I don't see a Buddha prophet, or a Muhammad prophet, or a Hindu prophet, or even satanists'prophets.

00:04:37.518 --> 00:04:51.574
They're all charismatic prophets, non-denominational, out there on YouTube prophesying. It's very alarming after a while. I said, 'Lord, help me.

00:04:51.575 --> 00:05:09.119
I know you called me to do this, but I don't want to be lumped in that crowd.'I separate myself from some of this because it's getting intense.

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:29.819
There's going to be a lot of this exposed in the coming days. I ain't here to point fingers at anybody and say that one is false. You need to line it up with the Word.

00:05:29.820 --> 00:05:42.433
If they're talking about scripture, leading you to pray, or teaching you how to fast and stand against the devil in the power and authority that's in you, then fine, follow them.

00:05:42.434 --> 00:05:47.422
But if they just have something popping a word out all the time, see if it follows the Bible.

00:05:47.423 --> 00:06:01.962
If it's just some random thought, be very watchful of who you're listening to.

00:06:01.962 --> 00:06:14.001
I had one girl in the comments ask if I saw what another girl said in her prophetic word.

00:06:14.002 --> 00:06:19.978
She was telling me all this stuff, and I had never heard of this person, so I went to look.

00:06:19.979 --> 00:06:28.973
Oh my gosh, this is so off. This is wrong. I looked and they have a ton of subscribers.

00:06:28.974 --> 00:06:39.146
They're leading these people, and I'm thinking, 'No, this is not good.'There are a lot of bad voices out there.

00:06:39.147 --> 00:06:44.831
I started looking at some of these voices and realized they're listening to familiar spirits.

00:06:44.832 --> 00:06:55.895
A lot of people are listening to familiar spirits, and I hate to say that, but it's the truth. You need to be very watchful of who you're listening to.

00:06:55.896 --> 00:07:03.651
I'm not pointing names or fingers, and I'm not going to call out because I'm not trying to do that; that's wrong.

00:07:03.652 --> 00:07:13.183
But I'm going to tell you this: you all need to have more discernment. You need to listen to and pray in the Spirit more.

00:07:13.184 --> 00:07:18.082
You need to seek God for yourself and stop listening to a lot of this nonsense.

00:07:18.083 --> 00:07:22.978
Get in the Word and find scriptures to stand on for your life.

00:07:22.979 --> 00:07:33.719
Follow the voice of the Lord for your life; you don't need prophetic videos. You have the same Holy Ghost inside of you to lead you.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:48.380
A lot of this is just like fortune telling—going from fortune teller to fortune teller trying to find a prophetic word for whatever's going on.

00:07:48.381 --> 00:07:57.022
I want to teach you all about prayer, the Bible, your covenant, the blood of Jesus, and your authority.

00:07:57.023 --> 00:08:01.211
I want to teach you about the devil and what he's trying to do to your life to kill, steal, and destroy you.

00:08:01.212 --> 00:08:06.984
You need to understand who you are in Christ. God has put a call on your life.

00:08:06.985 --> 00:08:14.566
If you have a call on your life, this is why you are going through attacks. Some of it is because you've opened doors through sin.

00:08:14.567 --> 00:08:25.112
I see it in the comment section: people saying they live with their boyfriend but aren't having a sexual relationship.

00:08:25.113 --> 00:08:34.095
Is that okay? No, it's not okay. Like Joseph, you've got to flee from evil.

00:08:34.096 --> 00:08:41.699
When that lady was trying to seduce him, he stripped his robe off and busted out the door.

00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:54.613
Do not give the devil any place in your life. If that man is not able to put a ring on your finger, then God has somebody else.

00:08:54.614 --> 00:08:59.219
That's your Ishmael; do not stay with an Ishmael. Find your Isaac.

00:08:59.220 --> 00:09:04.119
There are so many people on here desperate for love and marriage.

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:18.419
You think you're going to turn them around? No, you're not. The Bible says do not be unequally yoked with unbelievers.

00:09:18.420 --> 00:09:33.081
Do not tie your horse to a bad cart. Follow God, and he has the right spouse for you. You don't want to tie yourself up with the world.

00:09:33.082 --> 00:09:41.325
You say you're going to pray and get him saved, but right now you're just fornicating.

00:09:41.326 --> 00:09:50.548
No, get out. Have respect for yourself. If you say you need him to help pay the bills, God is your supplier.

00:09:50.549 --> 00:10:05.819
He's going to take care of you. Don't fall and go to hell for sex or for a relationship that is not based upon Godly principles.

00:10:05.820 --> 00:10:14.999
Find somebody that loves the Word and will pray with you. Marriage is hard enough as it is, okay?

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:25.559
But if you don't have somebody there that, when you're down and having a bad report, you can grab their hands and pray with you and say, 'Man, I need you to pray with me.

00:10:25.560 --> 00:10:34.193
Honey, would you intercede with me? I'm overcoming.'Whether the kids are sick or whatever, we've got to pray, we've got to get in faith and believe.

00:10:34.194 --> 00:10:39.306
Well, 'I don't know anybody like that.'Find somebody there.

00:10:39.307 --> 00:10:46.880
It's okay. God's going to bring them. Start fasting, start making a list. I made a list. This is what I'm believing for.

00:10:46.881 --> 00:10:53.050
