Don't let her be a little Jezebel out sleeping around. God, I thank you, Lord, you keep her protected.'I pray for my life all the time as a ten-year-old.

00:11:40.016 --> 00:11:43.735
I grew up like that. I just interceded and that's what you're going to do as an adult.

00:11:43.736 --> 00:11:50.039
'Well, I've never done that before.'No, you can pray now: 'Father, I thank you, Lord, that you bring me a godly spouse.

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:52.853
Thank you, Lord, that you bring somebody that knows the Word.

00:11:52.854 --> 00:12:00.177
Thank you that they're hungry.'You want to go to church on Sundays; I don't have to drag them to church, drag them out, whatever.

00:12:00.178 --> 00:12:12.419
Please! And be a nag? You don't want to hook your horse up to a broken wagon. Follow the voice of God for your life.

00:12:12.420 --> 00:12:27.479
Then, whenever times get hard, you can lean on that person and they can lean on you, and you can be iron sharpens iron. You don't want a bozo. Don't settle for an Ishmael.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:41.106
