00:12:59.090 --> 00:13:06.592
Run for your life! We're in the end of the end here. This is not a time to be dumb.

00:13:06.593 --> 00:13:14.759
This is a time to know Jesus is coming. Stop living in compromise. Stop it!

00:13:14.760 --> 00:13:18.395
So I get on these rants and I'm trying to tell you all because I love you guys.

